  The parameter image_data_segments allows users to adjust the number of  
  data segments, that is used in the linker flag to build the 32-bit dbms 
  server image. 

  The default value is 4, the valid entries are :  
  3, 4, 5, 6, 7 and 8. 

  The unit is in segments (256Mb). 
